# Struktur Project (Merchant Closepay Expo)

## Monorepo

- **Root**: Expo app (iOS, Android, Web). Entry: `App.tsx` → `apps/merchant-base` (MerchantbaseApp).
- **packages/core**: Auth, config, theme, i18n, account, navigation, notification, security. Platform logic; re-exports experience-core. Core tidak mengimpor dari app; icon quick menu disediakan app via setQuickMenuIconProvider(@experience-core).
- **packages/experience-core**: Tab/widget mapping, quick menu service, home tab settings, QuickMenuSettingsScreen, HomeTabSettingsScreen. Experience layer; depends on @core. Core re-exports these screens so app/navigation keep using @core/config.
- **packages/plugins**: Modul fitur merchant: balance, payment, invoice, catalog, order, fnb-merchant, kso. Setiap plugin punya `plugin.manifest.json` dan export lewat `index.ts`.
- **apps/merchant-base**: App merchant base; config di `config/app.config.ts`, screens & components di `src/`.

## Path Aliases (tsconfig + metro.config.js)

- `@core/*` → `packages/core/*`
- `@experience-core` / `@experience-core/*` → `packages/experience-core/*`
- `@plugins/*` → `packages/plugins/*`
- `@app/*` → `apps/merchant-base/src/*`

Gunakan alias ini untuk import; jangan relative path lintas package (mis. `import { useTheme } from '@core/theme'`).

## Konvensi Folder per Package

- **Core/Plugin**: `components/`, `services/`, `hooks/`, `models/`, `types/`. Screens di `components/screens/` atau `components/<feature>/`.
- **Plugin**: `plugin.manifest.json` di root plugin; `index.ts` re-export types, services, components.
- **App**: `src/screens/`, `src/components/`, `config/` (app.config, theme.color).

## Menambah Plugin Baru

1. Buat folder `packages/plugins/<pluginId>/` dengan `plugin.manifest.json` dan `index.ts`.
2. Di plugin: export default `createPluginModule(manifest, componentLoaders)` dari `index.ts`; tambah plugin ke `apps/merchant-base/bootstrap/plugins.ts` (import + tambah ke `registerPlugins([...])`).
3. Aktifkan di app config: `enabledModules` di `apps/merchant-base/config/app.config.ts`. Bentuk disarankan object (`Record<string, boolean>`); daftar ID ambil lewat `getEnabledModuleIds(config.enabledModules)`.
